        "@value": "Disney&#8217;s High School Musical"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "&lt;p&gt;We’re all in this together with Disney’s High School Musical ON STAGE! as Ignite Theatre students perform catchy songs, iconic dance steps and encourage others to stand firm in their identity and use their talents in multiple ways.&lt;/p&gt;\\n"
      }
