        "@value": "Chilliwack Comedy Classic 2026"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Back by popular demand!  Chilliwack’s signature pro standup comedy event returns in September.  \r\n\r\nEnjoy an evening with Canada’s BEST comedians live from your city’s amazing theatre.  Audiences can expect to see FRESH LINEUPS and occasional returning favourites:)\r\nLineup to be announced.  "
      }
